\"font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">, Ю.С. Ахмадулина</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:auto;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:0pt;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">ФГБОУ </span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">ВО</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;«Ивановский государственный политехнический университет», г. Иваново, Российская Федерация</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:center;page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:auto;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:0pt;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;\">Применение технологии </span><span style=\"font-size:16pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';lang:EN-US;font-weight:bold;\">Blockchain</span><span style=\"font-size:16pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;\">&nbsp;в </span><span style=\"font-size:16pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;\">авторском праве?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:auto;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:35.45pt;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Блокчейн</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;—</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;это</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;выстроенная по определённым правилам непрерывная последовательная цепочка блоков, содержащих информацию.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:auto;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:35.45pt;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">З</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">аписи объед</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">иняются в «блоки», которые</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;связываются </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">к</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">риптографически</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;в «цепочку» с помощью сложных математических алгоритмов. Каждый блок связан с предыдущим и содержит в себе набор записей. Новые блоки всегда добавляются строго в конец цепочки.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:auto;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:35.45pt;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Процесс шифрования, известный как хеширование, выполняется большим количеством разных компьютеров работающих в одной сети.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;Такие узлы сети называются </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">майнерами</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;Если в результате их расчетов все они получают одинаковый результат, то блоку присваивается</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;уникальная цифровая подпись</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">. Как только реестр будет обновлён и образован новый блок, он уже больше не может быть изменён. Таким образом подделать его невозможно. К нему можно только добавлять новые записи. Важно учесть то, что реестр обновляется на всех компьютерах в сети одновременно.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Heading-3\" style=\"text-align:justify;page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:auto;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:35.45pt;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">SciPaperChain</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;– </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">программа</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">,</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;построенная на основе этой технологии, позволяет хранить научные статьи, закрепляя их за автором.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;Пользователь загружает свою статью в </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">p</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">2</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">p</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">сеть, копия сохраняется на компьютерах сети в зашифрованном виде. Другие пользователи сети могут только просматривать те</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">кст ст</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">атьи, но не могут редактировать её.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Heading-3\" style=\"text-align:justify;page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:auto;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:35.45pt;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">Технология </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">blockchain</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;применяется во многих областях: </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">авторство и право владения, ц</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">ифровая идентичность, проверка подлинности и подтверждение прав доступа</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">,</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;э</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">нергетика</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">, </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">с</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">редства электронного голосования, элект</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">р</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">онные валюты и многое другое.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;(скрин)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Heading-3\" style=\"text-align:center;page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:auto;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:1;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:0pt;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-language:RU-RU;font-weight:bold;\">Библиографический список</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:auto;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:0pt;font-size: 14pt;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&#xa0;</span></p>\r\n</div></body></html>"}}]